headline: OpenAI’s Golden Touch Spreads as Stocks Soar Off Mere Mentions
summary: The company behind ChatGPT held its annual developers event Monday, and mere mentions of other publicly traded firms by presenters sent those shares soaring.  Online travel companies also saw brief pops, with Expedia Group, Inc., and TripAdvisor Inc., both advancing at least 7%.
